description:

I don't know about you, but I'm a sucker for some before and after picture collages. These are some of my favorites.  If you're not familiar with the concept, it's quite simple. it's a mashup of hardcore photos mixed with standard ones you'd see onprofiles and in pictureframes, all of the same girl. These are mostly amateur, due to the nature of the style. The photos are predominantly blowjob, but there's plenty of penetration throughout the set, a few MMF photos and and the occasional interracial snapshot. Most of the shots are taken by a handheld camera to add to the amateur aesthetic of it all
